  "title": "Food Processing Engineer",
  "description": "<p>We are from central kitchen in food manufacturing sector located in Singapore, fostering a positive work environment—\"Work Hard, Play Hard!\" We're looking for passionat professionals to join our family!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Position:</strong> Food Processing Engineer</p>\n<p><strong>Monthly Salary:</strong> From $2,500 onwards</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Operate food processing machines and equipment according to guidelines.</li>\n  <li>Follow standard operating procedures for food production and packaging.</li>\n  <li>Maintain hygiene and cleanliness in the production area.</li>\n  <li>Monitor product quality and report any issues to supervisors.</li>\n  <li>Assist in raw material preparation and product assembly.</li>\n  <li>Adhere to workplace safety and food hygiene standards.</li>\n  <li>Pack, label, and store finished products appropriately.</li>\n  <li>Perform routine maintenance and cleaning of machinery.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Ability to follow instructions and work efficiently in a fast-paced environment.</li>\n  <li>Physically fit and able to handle repetitive tasks.</li>\n  <li>Understanding of food hygiene and safety procedures.</li>\n  <li>Willingness to work in shifts and overtime when needed.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Why Join Us?</strong></p>\n<p>✔ 20 days of paid leave</p>\n<p>✔ Medical benefits &amp; insurance coverage</p>\n<p>✔ Various allowances &amp; incentives (Meal allowances, Revenue Incentives, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Various bonuses (AWS, performance, attendance)</p>\n<p>✔ Various rewards (Best Employee Award, Long services award, etc.)</p>\n<p>✔ Strong career progression opportunities</p>\n<p>✔ Revenue incentives</p>\n<p>✔ Sponsored courses for career growth</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>If you’re the right fit for our team, send your application here! We look forward to your application!</strong></p>",
